 generated by the population gradient. With NGC 6166 we\nappear to be penetrating into a regime of high enough galaxy mass and rich\nenough environment that the bimodal two-phase description of GC formation is no\nlonger as clear or effective as it has been in smaller galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Nov 2015 20:23:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-27"}
