tion, an\nenhancement is seen around $\\sqrt{s} =$ 4.42 GeV. Fitting the cross section\nwith a coherent sum of the $\\psi(4415)$ Breit-Wigner function and a phase space\nterm, the branching fraction $\\mathcal{B}(\\psi(4415)\\to\\omega\\chi_{c2})$ is\nobtained to be of the order of $10^{-3}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Nov 2015 06:12:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Jun 2016 06:25:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-01"}
