 amiable for simulating different physical process. The\ntools developed in this article for the analysis of the CA are easily\nextendible to the study of other one dimensional dynamical systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Nov 2015 13:18:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-04"}
